<h2 class="bac">Overview:</h2>  
<br>
<H3 class="bac">Sales</H3>
<p class="bac">
Our <u>Debt Profile</u> includes Interest Rate Products, Foreign Exchange, Commodities, Investment Grade, Leverage Finance, Mortgage and Asset Backed Products, as well as Structured Securities.  Our <u>Equity Profile</u> includes Equity Cash, Equity Derivatives and Electronic Trading Services. 
</p>
<br>
<H3 class="bac">Trading</H3>
<p class="bac">
Our <u>Debt product areas</u> include Interest Rate Products, Foreign Exchange, Commodities, Investment Grade, Leverage Finance, Mortgage and Asset Backed Products, as well as Structured Securities.  Our <u>Equity product areas</u> include Listed, Over-the-Counter and Derivative Securities. Bank&nbsp;of&nbsp;America Securities covers a wide array of industry sectors in both the Debt and Equity markets.
</p>
<br>
